        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3050197391" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6963438989236200842">This is the most powerful book I read all year. A prison narrative focusing on survival, human connection amidst a sea of suffering, and redemption, this book belongs in the annals of history alongside Elie Weizel’s “Night” and similar narratives. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


