<div id="review_3366905701" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3366905701" />
    <a title="Fouad Hamad" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/54880982-fouad-hamad"><img alt="Fouad Hamad" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1588356027p2/54880982.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3366905701?book_show_action=true">May 31, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Fouad Hamad" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Fouad Hamad" href="/user/show/54880982-fouad-hamad">Fouad Hamad</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3366905701" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1497733556283784463">I still can&apos;t fathom how I actually finished this book. honestly it broke me and made me question all aspects of life and the amount of cruelty in this world and to know that there are actually people that suffered in some unimaginable ways and some that are still experiencing these acts of madness is something that will never sit right with me.</span>
  <span id="freeText1497733556283784463" style="display:none">I still can't fathom how I actually finished this book. honestly it broke me and made me question all aspects of life and the amount of cruelty in this world and to know that there are actually people that suffered in some unimaginable ways and some that are still experiencing these acts of madness is something that will never sit right with me.</span>
